title: Premiere: SEYD – Secrets
body:
Birmingham teenager **SEYD** impressed on her debut offering; the punchy, CHVRCHES-esque This Ain’t Easy, and has now followed it up with the equally as alluring _Secrets_.

Again recalling elements of Lauren Mayberry’s pitch perfect vocal, Secrets is another glittering, chorus orientated number, showcasing the colossal potential that eighteen year old SEYD carries into 2017.

Like this? Follow our [On Repeat Playlist](https://open.spotify.com/user/crackintheroad/playlist/1UB6gJIZpmiO0H2zmSbg02) for a handpicked selection of the very best in new music; updated weekly.
